Rule: Marital Status: Married or Divorced is more favorable than Widowed
Gender: Male is more favorable than Female
Hours per Week: Working significantly more hours (e.g., 79 hours) is more favorable
Education Level: Having a Doctorate or Masters is more favorable than Some-college
Age: Being younger (e.g., 41 years old) is more favorable than being older (e.g., 63 years old)
